WEBVTT

step-1-intro
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.899
Welcome to Cutroom
This is Foley's Cutroom, where auto-generated product walkthrough videos land for review.

step-2-browse_folders
00:00:05.341 --> 00:00:11.390
Project folders
Every connected repo gets its own folder, showing step counts, takes, and who last touched it.

step-3-open_walkthrough
00:00:11.993 --> 00:00:18.054
Open a walkthrough
Opening the Foley project reveals the full walkthrough Foley built automatically from pull request activity.

step-4-review_steps
00:00:18.565 --> 00:00:23.998
Review the steps
Each step is a short clip with narration Foley generated to match the code change in that PR.

step-5-approve_take
00:00:24.509 --> 00:00:31.347
Approve and ship
Once you approve a take, Foley stitches the clips into a finished video and keeps it current with every new PR.
